<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jareck</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-07 19:01:36</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This pack is indeed a 25% reduction, not the absurd 70% claimed earlier.  There are three named orcs that spawn there, not two.  The SBH, Shralock Pack, and a totem that gives the divine aura effect are dropped depending on the orc's name.  As said earlier, the orc's name is Shralock something and is np for a group of 17-20's.  I was 17 or 18 when I got mine and it conned red to me at the time.  It works really well especially outside of paw with the fs greatstaffs and 2h swords that drop.<BR>
<BR>
Jareck Thundershot<BR>
25th season Ranger<BR>
The Majestic Knights of Norrath</font></td></tr></table>
