<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I've been camping orcs for about a week and the names of two of the orcs are Hagnis Shralok (drops SBH), and Vopuk Shralok (drops Shiny Brass Totem). I've never seen a third one so I can't comment on that but there are many higher level kill-stealers in HPH, so if you see someone who's not in a group kinda hanging around, and they won't give you a reason why they're watching the spawn, petition a GM to come watch so they get nailed. GMs can watch what goes on without appearing so let one know what's going on and they'll take care of it all.</font></td></tr></table>
