<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Warpig</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-24 16:53:22</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This bag is a pretty rare drop.  The camping on the HH orc side is kind'a tricky.  There will often be 2 or 3 groups there.  It is a free for all area most of the time.  So... it isn't actually kill stealing going on, but it is a volatile area that can be frustrating.  Also, if you are a higher level character wanting one of these bags, buy it.  You will find it hard to out-damage the groups in the area if it is free for all, and you won't be able to group because of experience issues.<BR>
<BR>
Warpig Fenrir<BR>
Pain Merc's of Scilence</font></td></tr></table>
